reviewText: This is old school film making at it's best. A who's done it, to a who's doing it. Lots of sexy scenes in this Hot Properties thriller. But in between the sheets there is a story you can follow and the ending satisfied me. I watch a lot of crap on NetFlix and then the movie just ends for no apparent reason and you just wasted and hour and half of your life. Grab some popcorn, turn off your cell phones and enjoy joy yourself into an Illusion of Sin.
the dvd is brand new - everything is ok. just the movie doesn't worth the waste of the blank dvd :)
